headline: Garmin teams up with Truemed to unlock HSA/FSA funds for fitness products
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) is teaming up with healthcare payments provider Truemed to help qualified customers tap into pre-tax HSA/FSA funds for reimbursement of qualifying purchases of fēnix®, Forerunner®, Instinct®, Lily®, Venu®, vívoactive® and vívosmart® smartwatches and fitness trackers, as well as Tacx® cycling trainers and Edge® cycling computers.
